  "They are coming.
   Atom by atom... they will coil around us...
   and take all that we are.
   There is one way to confront this threat.
   By reuniting the 24 warring Houses of our own empire.
   We have forgotten the Unforgettable...
   the last to unify our tribes - Kahless -
   together, under one creed... remain Klingon!
   That is why we light our beacon this day. To assemble our people.
   To lock arms against those whose fatal greeting is..."

The speech concludes with the words (in Federation Standard): "We come in peace."

These lines about Kahless were repeated in several episodes of {Star Trek Discovery:src} (with minor variations, see below).

